class:: GLPlayVid
summary:: plays a video loaded on the server.
related:: Classes/GLPlayImg, Classes/GLShowImgTex, Classes/GLShowVidTex
categories:: UGens>Video


Description::

Plays a video loaded on the server represented by a video ID.


classmethods::

method::fr

argument::vidID
The video with this ID is played.


Examples::

code::

// load a video on the server and play it
(
~vidID = 0;
GLVideo.new(~vidID, "/path/to/video.mp4");

{ GLPlayVid.fr(~vidID) }.play;
)

::
